Reference

Live Arena

Functions used to create and run live version of Arena

arena_new()

Creates arena object

arena_push_model()

Adds model to arena

arena_push_observations()

Adds new observations to arena

print(<arena_live>)

Prints live arena summary

arena_run()

Run server providing data for live Arena

Static Arena

Functions used to create and upload JSON file for Arena

arena_new()

Creates arena object

arena_push_model()

Adds model to arena

arena_push_observations()

Adds new observations to arena

print(<arena_static>)

Prints static arena summary

arena_upload()

Upload generated json file from static arena
